@PawPal.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5237

### Login to get JWT token (use your test user credentials)
POST {{PawPal.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "YourPassword123!"
}

### Get Chat Token (use the JWT from login response in Authorization header)
GET {{PawPal.Api_HostAddress}}/api/chat/token
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

